sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Deaf/HoH user
  participant B as Browser (MediaPipe)
  participant S as Socket.IO server
  participant E as ASLService / Predictor
  participant L as LLM provider chain
  U->>B: sign in front of webcam
  B->>B: MediaPipe Holistic → 543 landmarks
  B->>B: EMA smooth + compact payload
  B->>S: sign_start {language, w, h}
  S-->>B: sign_ready
  loop every frame (~20 fps)
    B->>S: sign_frame {frame}
    S->>S: append to 60-frame buffer
    alt buffer >= 6 and not busy
      S->>E: predict_sign(frames) [threadpool]
      E-->>S: (label, confidence)
      S->>S: majority vote (2/3) + cooldown
      opt vote accepted
        S-->>B: sign_detected {word, confidence}
      end
    end
  end
  B->>S: POST /api/translate/sentence {gloss[]}
  S->>L: gloss→sentence (few-shot, cached)
  L-->>S: natural sentence
  S-->>B: {sentence, source}
  B-->>U: caption + optional speech (TTS)
